It might still be too early, but she would still like you to be the first witness to this snow-washed spring.

Name: Silver White
WorldDescription: A dress as white as silver snow, as the love of Winter Sonata. The pure white figure chuckles in the snow and the faint flush on her cheeks dispels the cold winter altogether. It jogs the memories of summer days when lavender was in full bloom, recording the everlasting ripples of this moment.

Name: Deed of Snow Leopard
WorldDescription: What can I do for you, Commandant...? Wait! Why am I still doing this? Although there is anger in the girl's eyes, she will only bare her fangs when she tries to protect her allies. She will also try her best to temporarily disguise herself for missions. And of course, she won't let anyone take her most important away from her.

Name: Bloody Love
WorldDescription: Afraid of needles? But you won't get better without a little jab... C'mon, trust your nurse on this. It won't hurt a bit. Pain, pain, blow away! Till the ends of Milky Way!

But in the end, everyone is infected by her cheerfulness. Perhaps she will jump out from the sea when you are unprepared and enthusiastically shout, "Aloha!"

""The children of Neverland can be carefree only because they don't know the ocean's wrath. The real guardian of dreams would face the storm with them and guard them until they grow up!"

WorldDescription: Designed by Ayla herself and in her favorite colors, this cute driving costume also enhances the frame's protection ability against impacts.

Name: Lost Butterfly
WorldDescription: Parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme... The witch picks colors from the forest and blends them into her magic along with the undying melody, the eternal hope, and the rainbow-color fantasy. Therefore, the winged fairies leave traces of dancing on the paper and travel beyond the raging storms to lead the seekers to where the melody of the magic pipe comes from.

Equipped with special expansion "Illusion", it can create a simulacrum of the Construct with similar energy level and physical form, which can come in handy in many situations as a special tactical module. The fluorescent components are said to be proud works of WGAA.

Name: Grace
WorldDescription: Amazing Grace, how sweet the sound. She had witnessed many lives stepping into the divine hall. Never had she thought that one day that she could wear this outfit herself, as you took her hand in the blessed light.

Name: Spring Huntress
WorldDescription: Inspired by a royal spring hunting tradition thousands of years ago, this coating combines the traditional archer costume with the aristocratic clothing style. It dispels misfortune and misery that imprison the world with the sound of the deities and brings back spring.

Name: Starry Desert
WorldDescription: A coating inspired by Sophia's memories of Akdilek. It gives a feeling of the sand sea and the clear starry night outside the train, making Sophia feel like being at Akdilek.

Name: Mandala Dance
WorldDescription: A coating design based on the traditional Akdilek costumes that wraps Sophia's body in gossamer with gold ornaments rustling at each moment and a six-petalled camellia slowly blossoming at her waist. With her reposed visage, the audience watches in stunned splendor at her elegant and just manner.

It is equipped with high-density creature filters, and the special boosters installed in its arms and legs provide formidable burst power and dexterity.

Name: Golden Days
WorldDescription: A dress-like Coating made for commercial infiltration missions. The suitcase has weapons hidden within, and the inner layer is made from bullet-proof materials using a special technique. It has maintained a glamorous and agile look without compromising on defense.

Name: Dance of Ripplets
WorldDescription: Hiding her scales and leaving the ocean, she has sacrificed much, and she has finally met that person. Right now, with her feet on the ground, her arms move with her dress, dancing before the figure. Even knowing that it might all turn into bubbles and disappear in the end, she just wishes to dance for the one she cares deeply about, whose heart she is hoping to touch—the same way hers was touched when they first met.

Name: Vermillion Bargain
WorldDescription: She turns her back against the gods in the deepest night and chants the forbidden spell with her life. Flickering candlelight sways over her familiar face. No matter how long you have parted from each other, the pact and oath you made will eventually light up the lost memories, bringing back everything that was once lost. "...I have come to fulfill the Crimson Pact."

WorldDescription: Themed around the punk fashion in the Golden Age, it is merely a decorative coating that will not improve the combat ability. However, it does give you an impulse to jump on the stage, sing your lungs out, and smash a guitar.

Name: Agony Break
WorldDescription: Blooming in a cage where mercy is not allowed to exist, a flower of solitude colors her enemies who are afraid of even meeting her gaze in a sweet, scarlet red. Before she bestows a release of death, she takes in the pain that will linger on within her forever. "Fleeting salvation is but a pale illusion, only pain sustains an everlasting vividness."

Name: Yaksha Undertow
WorldDescription: An oriental style coating that resembles the traditional garment people usually wear for ceremonies. Together with his unusual Inver-Device, Camu looks quite like a ghoul, an intimidating creature in the legends of the Golden Age.

Name: Guard of Hell
WorldDescription: Guarding the burning door of hell, he is often seen as an ominous sign of death. The living are scared to look at him when passing by, and he also gives them a fierce look in return. But the living never know how dedicated he is to his post and how many times he has escorted those who haven't reached the time of death out of the hell before Halloween night.

Name: Prince of Darkness
WorldDescription: A crack breaks among the chaos deep down in the river Styx. The demon king wakes up from his long sleep. His once restrained might started to flow around him. Curses trickle from the corner of his eyes. Generations of seals come off from his back. He moves his knuckles, finally, turning his gaze to the person kneeling before the throne. Time to pay the price for waking up the demon king.

Name: Howling Crown
WorldDescription: When all things are silent, she still holds the shining spear up high, for she vows to protect, save, and uphold this world with dignity. You are the first to discover her in the snow.

Name: Niki US1000
WorldDescription: Power system online, wind-pressure balance calibrated, GPS configuration completed... Would you guide me to claim victory in battle once again?

Name: Ginkgo Ridge

But when the victim found their backpack and wanted to thank him, he was nowhere to be found, leaving behind only a golden ginkgo leaf. "No need to thank me—I was just passing by."" ...The victim turned the leaf over and saw an address with a line of text. ""Or, if you like, come visit this shop and make the old man happy. Everything is guaranteed to be fairly priced."

Qu does not have many opportunities to wear this outfit, but she still hopes this indispensable part of Tabula Akasha can be shown to the world.

WorldDescription: With young and frivolous as the main concept of the design, the coating shows the rebellion and self of the lone wolf girl. Just standing at the corner of the street in this dress, it seems that it can release an aura that strangers are not allowed to approach.

Name: Fiery Moon
WorldDescription: The fantasy of the pale moon has sealed the false god's grace, for it scorns lives fallen into corruption. She needs no daylight for her glory. With a mere gesture of hers, the ruins of a shattered sanctum will rise anew. Travelers back to the world, have you captured the light fleeting in her eyes?

Description: Strike Hawk HQ Attire — Wanshi: Hypnos
WorldDescription: Modified from Strike Hawk's uniform Coating to adapt to Wanshi's flexible combat style. The hawk is always on standby, both as a medic and as a warrior.

Name: Night Fume
WorldDescription: The moon hangs between the withered branches of the plane trees, and blood-red roses bloom on the ground. Common ravens fly across the dew-soaked cobblestone road as he places the salvation named soul's delivery against the forehead of the sinner. A prayer precedes the gunshot, but it offers no peace.

Name: Nightingale and Rose
WorldDescription: The nightingale thought you were the lover in her songs, so she pierced her chest with thorn, then handed you a rose bred from her blood... What happened after? You gilded the rose and put it behind her ear.

Name: Aria of Nymph
WorldDescription: A fae of the sea, resting by the distant shore, singing along the waves. She blesses the hero, helps the travelers, and protects the warriors from harm. But she never leaves this place, turning the waves into her garment, guarding a dream far, far away.

Name: Honor Model
WorldDescription: The custom-made uniform of the outstanding graduates of F.O.S. It is close-fitting but does not impede movement, flashy but not ostentatious, suitable for attending various occasions. The pure gold chain presiding on the chest always reminds the dresser to shoulder the mission of the elite, to hang the honor and responsibility on the heart, and to become a glorious example to lead the crowd.

Name: Nosferatu
WorldDescription: Drink a glass of redness in the dark night in admiration of all beings. No longer accepted by the light, he will still protect you quietly in the darkness.

Name: Radiant Respite
WorldDescription: Even though he was not the initiator, he managed to give you a trip that was perfect for you. With the stars coming out above, he smiles under a street lamp, waving his hand. A night breeze gently puts a period on this date of yours, but before saying your goodbyes, you lightly readjust his slipping scarf. He would never have thought such a trivial move is already enough to make an ever-cool-headed person like him skip a heartbeat.

Name: Red Hoodie
WorldDescription: The coating was designed based on a fairy tale. Short skirts, bows, petite red hood. The naive girl doesn't know the meaning of this dress, nor has she considered why she needs to "dress up."" However, when she sees others smile at her, she always feels ""warm."

Name: Solar Frost
WorldDescription: Her white figure is surrounded by wild drum beats like the snow in the scorching summer. Amid the waves, she sings gently. It seems as if the nursery rhyme is going to calm the waves of the rock music and flow straight ahead. Skills, thoughts, and the soul she infuses into her singing are as ethereal as the snow in the summer. Nevertheless, the audience is still cheering for this petite snowflake.

Name: Silent Seal
WorldDescription: The Silent Seal cannot be taken seriously. Made from Kowloong folklore, this Coating was said to be the reward for No. 21's performance in an event. "A new haunted house just opened in the shopping street and the owner asked me to be an actress. I didn't have to do much, apart from jumping out and smiling at the visitors. I did a great job."

Name: Generic
WorldDescription: The default outfit given to Constructs when they were manufactured.

Name: Generic - Final

Name: Sorrowful Rose
WorldDescription: The black veil is for hiding her deadly intent, concealing her in the night. The thorns are there to remind her of her pain, a penance to her sins. The brand is to imprint her with the promise she must keep. "May her soul rest in slaughter..."

Name: Wavebender
WorldDescription: She has reduced her armor to the minimum to make sure that she can surf freely in the feast of music. However, what interests her more is to lie under a sunshade and watch how helpless you are until she calls you when the time's right, "Commandant, get that for me." As a reward, she will share the small space under her sunshade with you.

Name: Mesektet
WorldDescription: She is a radiant sun that unfurls the banner to illuminate the darkness. She is the winds of the underworld that howl across the sky to mark the border between life and death. She is the vanguard of the gods, the leader of heroic souls, the deity silently awaiting the long night. When the sun sets and the sacred ibis spreads its wings, will you join her in an eternal expedition to defend the oath sworn by both of you?

Name: Grandiose Glamor
WorldDescription: Her lance can break through any formation; her horse has trampled over the western land. "Once upon a time, there was a valiant female general who had achieved countless merits. After retiring from the royal guards, she became a guardian of Babylonia city, bringing doom upon all thieves and bandits. The civilians finally had a peaceful life, and everybody was delighted..." —Tales of the Babylonia Legends

Name: Generic
WorldDescription: The default coating given to the Construct.

Name: Generic - Modified
WorldDescription: The enhanced coating given to the awakened Construct.

Name: Generic - Final
WorldDescription: The ultimate coating given to the Construct who reaches the Ultima Rank.

Name: Fool's Fables
WorldDescription: Clapping! Whistle! Bravo! The clown hears loud noises. He jumps through fire, escapes from the beast, dances on the border of danger, hoping that his audience can be amazed and give him a round of applause. The next moment, the show has ended and the curtain falls. —There is no audience.

Name: Billowing Indigo
WorldDescription: Plain clothes partly dyed in cloudy ink, an indigo sash, and a tuft of tied hair dangling in the wind. Having lived half his life in a cage, plumes of smoke break him from his confines. Thoughts of good and evil torment his heart. Gratitude, resentment, love, and hatred—all bear witness to laughter. Casting aside conflicting interests, his pursuits begin to bear fruit.

Name: Generic
WorldDescription: The default outfit given to Constructs when they were manufactured.

Name: Wings of Dawn
WorldDescription: Legend says humans couldn't endure through the long night. So, they gathered the sparkles and shimmers of their life forces, and together they weaved a pair of feather wings for their god. The god took the wings and ascended to the sky, becoming the stars and shone light upon the earth so that humans could see daylight again. What about the god, you say? Well, the god... Even now, the god is still watching us from thousands of miles away, alone in a cold place.

Name: Dreamcatcher
WorldDescription: The fairytale dream hidden in the corner of the spire is watching over the child in sleep. Though far away from the child it once guards, the forest itself will still be the first to pick up the child when she gets lost. The green fluorescence indicates where the wind comes from, and wings spread in the sea of flowers. She takes a nap here without going anywhere.

Name: Irisfall Ballad
WorldDescription: Not knowing how many years she has been waiting and entangled in thorns, Iris is finally bathed in the bright sunlight and bloom in front of the one that she has been missing for so long. However, when that person reaches the flower, the pedals suddenly fall and become dust, leaving only a faint singing lingering in the dream.

Name: Vox Solaris
WorldDescription: She gazes at the morning dew at dawn and starry sky at night. When spring arrives, she wanders along the melting river; when autumn comes, she touches the fallen petals. On rainy days, the girl plays her music alone in the secluded temple, waiting for the sun to rise again. Accompanied by the sky and four seasons, she grasps the remaining fragments. No matter how far they are apart from each other and if the world responds to her invocation, she will keep praying for the one she misses. The rain gradually eases off in the sound of her flute. When dawn comes, the bell rings too. When the sky clears, flowers will bloom again.

Name: Flowing Dreams
WorldDescription: Although Selena has never tried anything like it before, this coating feels tailor-made for her. Unlike the vague recollections of her usual attire, it allows for effortless movement and running, while also possessing the uncanny ability to uplift her spirits. Could it be that the designer of this coating intended to reveal a new facet of Selena? Hoping to witness her radiant smile by the seaside, accompanied by a joyous melody sung from her heart?

Name: Dragonwood
WorldDescription: A jade green dress that brings out the vitality of a girl with the vigor of nature and Tao by replacing intricate patterns with elegant calligraphy.

Name: Dreamweaver
WorldDescription: A Coating made based on Pulao's description of her dream. With great passion, Pulao described the tea room waiters, the old man who sold prune drinks, and the shop owner who recommended her this suit. "Char siu buns are the best!"" ""You look like an idol in this suit!" These sentences always echo in everyone's M.I.N.D. after Pulao's passionate interpretation.

Name: Night Navigator
WorldDescription: Featuring the design style of aviation devices in the Golden Age, it commemorates humanity's glorious journey from starting to know the universe to conquering the future and regeneration. When the girl ventures into the universe in this "coat armor," her determination goes without saying.

Name: Fantastical Fellowship
WorldDescription: Drink some tea and get some rest. Journey in the rabbit hole is full of danger. Singing won't waste your time, as the clock will stop at 6 o'clock. Why is a raven like a writing desk? Because I'll be with you no matter what.

Name: Maleficent
WorldDescription: Though she is the dark dragon that rules over the night sky, it is in this darkness that she lost everything. No one dares approach her deadly thorns, yet she long awaits their embrace.

Name: March Hare
WorldDescription: Out with the old, in with the new—the rabbit brings spring back. With her launcher gone, the girl stuffs "ammo" into her weapon, aims at the sky, and pulls the trigger to announce the arrival of spring. Wishes shoot across the sky; blessings boom through the air. Under the night sky ablaze with blossoming fireworks, a fleeting light graces the window ledge. What dreams is this pensive rabbit quietly weaving?

Name: Neon Dynamite ☆
WorldDescription: In the radiant spotlight, let your dreams unfold; Eager ears listen, seeking where you behold. Each subtle motion can ignite the hidden emotion; Yet, in this moment, let your restless heart find resolution. Though it may not align with your every desire, ensure your hair's perfection; Are you ready? The dream stage awaits, just a single step away.

Name: Warding Ritualist
WorldDescription: On the Ghost Festival, the Earth Deity grants absolution. A young woman in a flowing Taoist robe walks along the ancient path, a cool night breeze ruffling her hair. Tonight, the gates of the underworld swing open. Spirits, nourished by the offerings of their descendants, wander aimlessly, searching for sustenance. The young woman shakes her bell, lays out food and drink, and offers blessings to guide the lost souls to peaceful rest. But some resentful spirits refuse to be appeased and seek to wreak havoc on the mortal world. Whenever she encounters one, she lets out a scornful laugh, swings her hammer with furious force, and roars, "Ingrates! I'll send you straight to oblivion!"

Name: Homecoming
WorldDescription: A mass-produced coating designed for daily life. The simple ornament reminds people of a librarian or a waiter. Although it's not costumed, it allows the user to adjust to the new life and the crowd.

Name: Summer Glimmer
WorldDescription: To take the "outcast" tag off themselves, Dark Aries decided to use rock-paper-scissors to find a lucky member, who would later take part in the beach talent show! Noan ended up as the unfortunate winner. Although he vowed not to disgrace the harmonica skills Watanabe taught him, on the day of rehearsal, he managed to infuriate the new teacher—who refused to disclose their name and identity—so much that they passed out three times within four hours. Will he really be able to perform...?

Name: Exorcist
WorldDescription: The exorcist's lamp shines bright before her chest with her silver blade reflecting her beautiful face. With her golden eyes fixed on the shadow of the past, she will eventually find out the truth at the end of the dark realm.

Name: Solitary Dream
WorldDescription: Dreams stir; snowflakes bloom. Sighs awaken sleeping shards, leading dreamers to a snow-kissed church. Saints pray here—even if the gods remain silent, just having you listen is enough. When the forgotten loves and flowers bloom once more, she will return to this place, waiting with a smile for the one who swore an oath to her.

Name: Pyrewatch
WorldDescription: When the crimson wind howls, searing flames consume the fallen sinners and dye her clothes as she wanders between destruction and oblivion, granting inevitable endings to all tangible existences. With her blade, she vows to burn all demons to ashes and make souls rest, bringing equal peace to all the departed.

Name: Swan Lake
WorldDescription: Inspired by Bambinata's ballet dress back from her childhood, it is a coating Vanessa specially made for Bambinata. The little swan in the dream has eventually responded to echoes from the past, rising up onto her toes and dancing in the new castle once again. Bambinata might not know why she was given such an exquisite coating, but in a certain corner of her M.I.N.D., a shard of shattered glass has melted away without a trace.

Name: Catwalk
WorldDescription: A gear turns, a chime rings, and the cozy wooden hut becomes a cradle. The soft purring weaves a new dance melody.When Bambinata gently calls Azuki's name to awaken it from its slumber, she knows there is no need to define the "friendship" between them—for all that matters is she wants to stay with the graceful little feline.

Name: Dreamland Waltz
WorldDescription: The curtains part amid thundering instrumental clangs. With neon ribbons cascading from above and fireworks blooming across the sky, a girl pirouettes to the melody, leaping between the carousel's whirling steeds. Each of her steps sparks roars of rapture from the throng. This jubilant night refuses to slumber as long as her dance spins on.

Name: Scarlet Redeemer
WorldDescription: Soaked in the blood of his prey, he wanders in the rift between time and space. Mountains of bounties lie on the end of the burning night, but they cannot satisfy him. The hunter ticks the names on his list one after another. He has paid numerous prices, and will continue to do so. "Point me another possible solution before you accuse me."

Name: Diving Shadow
WorldDescription: Diving under the water immediately takes away all the hustle and bustle of life, leaving only the shimmering sunlight in tranquility. The ocean is free for explorers to wander, with endless beautiful things and scenes. One cannot help but want to capture and share these splendid moments with their most important ones, or invite them to swim in this very sea together. After all, wishes are no longer just wishes; they are within reach between the waves.

Name: Morningstar
WorldDescription: An artist, a fighter, or a commandant... with her paintbrush, she paints a myriad of her possible futures, each glimmering as brightly as the morning stars. It doesn't matter if her pace is hectic or not as long as each step she takes will carry her toward what she believes in. A colorful trail is left in her wake. She'll embrace each tomorrow with her best cheeky grin anywhere, anytime.

Name: Dazzler
WorldDescription: The keynote of the battlefield is not black, white, or gray! Every leap of the girl will be the strongest order in the battle game. With Ayla's favorite elements added to it, this super-mobile new coating is hands-down an eye-catcher on the battlefield.

Name: Blue Crush
WorldDescription: The cerulean ocean stretches to the horizon. Sunlight gently caresses the shimmering waves as a boat glides across this smooth canvas, leaving behind flickering ripples. On the beach, the rainbow-like girl waves the paintbrush in her hand, forever capturing the splendor of this azure world.

Name: Zhuolu's Rain
WorldDescription: Lightning rips the day; dark stars fall at night. Friendship, sacrifices, betrayals—she's ditched a lot but carries memories etched in her skin, a tapestry of ancient battles. It's her proof that "they" were real. As history turns to legends and myths get passed down, what kind of world now reflects in the eyes of this lone wanderer?

Name: Nightbreaker
WorldDescription: Another midnight, lightning and fire light up the raging storm... When all is peaceful again, the girl flips her wrist to sheath her blade. Before the wailing sirens arrive, she has already vanished at the end of the street. Nobody knows who she is; criminals call her the White Nightmare, while law enforcers identify her as a vigilante. The strong see her as trouble, while the weak call her a savior... But regardless of how the world may judge her, as long as evil continues to breed in the shadows where light cannot reach, she has never wavered in her mission to cut through the darkness.

Name: Vow of Dragon
WorldDescription: The dragon descends in the crimson light, the tiger heralds prosperity. She strides through desolate ruins and mountain peaks, with clouds gathering and trailing behind her scale armor and ignited pairing blades. The dragon is veiled, shifting, aloof, and enigmatic. Yet, the marks etched upon her hem carry the brilliance of fire, sealing within it a steadfast resolve she seldom reveals.

Name: Tsubaki
WorldDescription: On a moonless, silent night, a hint of crimson flashes through the snow-covered forest. Outside the grand hall, the three sins—greed, hatred, and delusion—manifest, bringing forth countless evils, while the sea of illusions and suffering grows. Undaunted, she severs all bonds. Her resolve, swift like thunder, scatters the cold frost. Ghosts and phantoms hide, and the true heart is found once more. Step by step, through the mountain's path, the crimson hue of camellias echoes like the final note of meditation.

Name: Stride of Vigor
WorldDescription: Height: 165cm Weight: 48kg Basal Energy Expenditure: ********MW Activity Consumption: Calculating... Daily Intake: Grilled fish x1, 279 kcal; Hiking sports electrolyte x2, 1100 kcal Fitness Guide: Unable to confirm whether high-intensity physical activity may cause negative effects on Construct functionality. User is advised to collect motion data and focus on optimizing the balance module. Undigestible water and food will be excreted through artificial texture on bionic skin. Would you like to activate the coating's cooling layer?

Name: Hunt of Retribution
WorldDescription: Like every urban legend tells it, she sets out when the night is darkest, leaving only the roar of her ride behind. Whether her journey ends in a rendezvous or a fight, she will find her answer before dawn.

Name: Heartseeker
WorldDescription: When the ghostly coffin is lifted, the lovebirds will return, so a long separation should not cause grief. When I lean on my pillow at midnight, my dance would shine among the stars. This stage costume is based on a popular novel in Kowloong and clearly reveals the type of work that its designer has been obsessed with lately. Finally reunited with the owner of this Coating, the girl designer proudly mentions that she has already prepared another costume with similar style. Who could she be planning to dress up...?

Name: Arboreal Slumber
WorldDescription: Fine silk, swallows’ call, and chic braids, hail the season of spring with great praise. With its flowing silken ribbons and fluent patterns, this specially tailored attire always stirs a dancer's heart, bringing nostalgic memories. She bids a somber farewell to the quaint alleys onstage, then sips green bamboo leaf wine after the curtain falls. Beneath the pavilion, as clouds part to reveal the moon, the ethereal mist makes her sober again. The vessels and mountains in her dream fade slowly into the new dawn.

Name: Little Lost Nightmare
WorldDescription: The innocent white is tainted by deep nightmares. This ferocious beast is lost in the cruel cage. No opponent has seen her true form, for the battle outcome is usually determined the moment the whistle blows. Remember to never blink when the beast of pale white and dark purple breaks free from the cage.

Name: Revival Remedy
WorldDescription: Her gown is white like snow, her dark teal robe dampened by morning dew. Wherever the miracle doctor visits, all diseases will go. "Have I told you about this doctor in Babylonia? Despite her young age, she has remarkable medical skills. A baby had been crying for three days, but stopped as soon as this doctor took one look at it. Everyone praises her as a reincarnation of the legendary doctor..." —Tales of the Babylonia Legends

Name: Tiny Bad Wolf
WorldDescription: The rays of the sun paint the theme park into a fairy tale wonderland. A little explorer weaves through the colorful balloons and the carousel. "I found a sparkly place. It has a lot of humans the same size as me. And a lot of fun things. The taste isn't bad either. I think you would like it too. Would you like to come with me?"

Name: Punk Dynamo
WorldDescription: Purchase in the Harvest Festival celebration of New Oakley, this outfit is said to be the classic attire of a legendary rock master. Noctis modified it into a new Coating more suitable for close-quarter combat after bringing it back to Babylonia. Despite having almost no opportunity to wear it, Noctis still displayed it in the most prominent place in the room. Soon after, rumors like "that Cerberus guy who liked dancing is getting even more into it" began to spread among squads. Of course, the rumor has been openly denied by that guy.

Name: Sky Rider
WorldDescription: He blazes through mountains and builds bridges on water. He helps those in need, but never leaves a name. "There was another street gangster whom nobody liked to mention his name. He lost an arm in a past accident, and replaced it with a prosthetic one. Still, he had a warm heart and always stood against injustice. Whenever he saw a rich brat bullying others, he would immediately clench his prosthetic fist and punch them in the face..." —Tales of the Babylonia Legends

Name: Nocturnal Watch
WorldDescription: The girl chases evil at midnight in the jungle of steel, guarding the city's night alone. Even when midnight has passed, she still presses down on the brim of her hat and knocks on the next hidden door, leaving a violet silhouette on the armor behind.

Name: Twilight Veil
WorldDescription: Under the orange sky, time freezes in the doomsday twilight. Everything decays and fades away. There is still hope. Even if the gods have abandoned the world, there are still stars that still shine their dim light to lead everyone back home.

Name: Sandy Spectrum
WorldDescription: Amidst the rhythm of waves crashing ashore, the girl leaps gracefully into the air. The pale violet silhouette flashes from behind, sending a spike through the air with precision. As the whistle blows, she and her sister exchange a smile and turn to face their opponents: "That was a warning for your foul."

Name: Generic - Final
WorldDescription: The outfit is modified by Constructs after they reach the [Advanced] awakening phase. Perfectly resembles the characteristics of their M.I.N.D.

Name: Abyssal Dye
WorldDescription: The sailors have come back with not only goods, but also legends. Some say she is a siren, luring humans to her beauty; some claim she is a guardian goddess, pointing direction to the lost vessels. When she leaps out of the sea, rainbow would follow; her tears hold the promise of miraculous healing and eternal life. Countless travelers have embarked on quests in search of these tears. However, what moves her heart to shed those drops?

Name: Solitary Longings
WorldDescription: A wandering fish drifts silently in her dream, gazing at the flickering light upon the shore. Waves rise and fall, shattering the illusions and devouring the false dreams. If only this fleeting moment could last forever... Could it capture the distant, unreachable light on the far-off waves for her?

Name: Carmine Ripples
WorldDescription: Known only to a few, a legend promises that mermaids who vault an emerald cascade will rise to divinity with scales sloughing away. A maiden drifts among her kin, yet her eyes cannot help but steal glances at the rainbow bridge behind with her mind ablaze with memories of clan oaths and ancestral chains. What worth is divinity if freedom lies beyond her grasp? In a surge of resolve, she turns around, plunging herself down from the bridge, toward the world of humanity.

Name: BRS
WorldDescription: Coating of Collab Character "BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER"

Name: Elder Flame
WorldDescription: Before the girl fell silent deep underground, her name was once known across the universe. Now with her eyes open once again, she has returned with a blazing blue flame, shattered chains, and roaring cannon. She is ready to ignite a new storm that will sweep across this place of endless conflicts.

Name: Sandstream
WorldDescription: With a free will, you walk into the wind and sand and explore every corner of the world. The desert you walk on was once a sea. The ruins you touch was once a magnificent palace. You look up upon the stars but end up seeing them vanishing. However, they will not be forgotten because of the moment you stopped by.

Name: Hell Sing
WorldDescription: The blades that once shielded the people and the legions that fought in Hell have collapsed and fallen beneath the shadow of the Sanctuary. The embers of the past spread with the wind as the "War Knight" gathers the flames and casts the decayed old world into the furnace. When the horns of doomsday are blown, the dead shall rise in search of vengeance, forging their final steel.

Name: Ashen Wings
WorldDescription: Above a tower surrounded by dark thorns, the girl activated a forbidden ritual to turn herself into an immortal existence, only to protect the people under her throne. A century has passed, and all her enemies have perished, yet the undying queen is still sitting on the throne in her desolate city, waiting for the next challenger to free her from the never-ending duty. Do you have the courage to accept her challenge?

Name: Resplendent Debut
WorldDescription: Opera performers take turns to come up on stage in elaborate costumes with their graceful movements and expressive singing drawing all eyes under the stage to them. In this moment, years of hard work off stage have paid off. The long history, the vast land, and the splendid world. Everything has been brought before the audience's eyes through the opera.

Name: Sparragon's Triumph
WorldDescription: On the day of the Sparragon's Triumph, all legions shall kneel in surrender. She stands before the shattered flagpole, the Gibbous Edge afloat in her palm. Her shoulder plates shape into bronze birds, her blade gleaming beneath lazuline feathers. Before the throne lie the fallen; behind it rises the glory of Kowloong. Dust shall be wiped away with blood - traitors, banished for eternity.

Name: Pixelpop
WorldDescription: Plug in the synth and turn on the amp. It is time to let the colors and music explode, so push aside your busy work on this rare holiday. Our rhythms will fill the streets, and our graffiti will speak our minds. Party on!

Name: Good Vibrations
WorldDescription: What matters most for a beach getaway? Waterproof sandals, surfboard wax, or sleek athletic swimwear? These may be essential, but so are the sun's tune, the waves' melody, and the comfort of soft sand beneath your feet. A harmonious resonance will only come from graceful movements.

Name: Blush of Daybreak
WorldDescription: A girl in colorful clothes wanders through the bustling streets with hot pastries in her hand. In the sound of firecrackers, she walks swiftly, spreading the happiness of a new year to every corner she reaches.

Name: Moonlight Soliloquy
WorldDescription: As the moon descends in the silver sky, she treads ice in a graceful veil, returning to the earth she left behind. Time races forward, yet at the end of all things, the girl halts her stride, turning back amidst the darkness to clasp your hand. The entire universe has gone silent as you stand together amidst the pale desolation.

Name: Crystalline Glance
WorldDescription: Her eyes, like the deep sea, shimmer with fragments of light—proof of a wandering heart seeking answers. The waves roll with the bubbles of freedom, and freedom is the color of the sea breeze. The cool, delicate threads of air graze her palms, reluctant to let that figure dissolve into the twilight. At the end of the glassy sea lies her riddle, her yearning, the memory she wishes to anchor in this moment.

Name: Tainted Moonrise
WorldDescription: Awake, the girl gently opens her eyes. Beneath a starry sky, her eyes glow not merely with the light of cosmic rivers, but also with a nascent spark that seems to ensnare souls. After enduring seemingly unending malevolence and countless nights of unease, she finally finds someone who is willing to step into her picture book, someone to share the breath of twilight and the golden plains at dawn. Unable to suppress the impulse in her heart any longer, she lifts her gaze, mustering her courage to take the hand by her side.

Name: Graffiti Code
WorldDescription: Bring all your graffiti spray cans and turn the rock music in your headphones all the way up. What comes next is a wild street party that lasts all night. "If we don't have our names all over this alley by sunrise, you lose."

Name: Ardent Trek
WorldDescription: "Across the barren wasteland, a fearless girl stands. She never fears the mechanical villains, helping the innocent civilians..." This popular ballad has accompanied her long journey. Though she is no longer the legendary protector of the wanderers, beneath her synthetic skin still beats a heart burning with passion.

Name: Radiant Formula
WorldDescription: The sun is high, the afternoon is hot, and the roar of engines, accompanied by the cheers of the crowd, shakes the racetrack like a storm. The racing cars chase each other relentlessly, like a streak of rainbow. The final turn is just ahead, and the leading driver, with a bright smile, slams on the brakes and turns the steering wheel sharply, leaving another mark of victory on the scorching track.

Name: Flying Apsara
WorldDescription: In the bright moonlight, she dances like a flying Apsara in celebration of peace to the ancient music. Her moves are elegant while her plucking of the strings is fast. Her dress flutters, stirring up ripples of the past and the present as if she's dancing in a dream that has lasted for a thousand years.

Name: River Dancer
WorldDescription: With lotus in her hair and golden threads flowing, she dances like a song—graceful, mesmerizing, dulling even the melody of falling plums. Each step across the water ripples with brilliance, echoing the serene drizzle over the pond. The painted boat vanishes amidst the lotus, yet the lingering breeze leaves traces upon the bright mirror—like the gentle glow in the dancer's eyes, or the whisper of the passing rain.

Name: Tapestry of Spring
WorldDescription: Ring out the old year and ring in the new with a new melody and the tapestry of spring. The girl infuses her best wishes into the window paper-cuts she made and put them up in the lingering coldness of the spring and the sound of firecrackers.

Name: Frosty Perch
WorldDescription: The wind howls as the snow blows, the perched owl resting in the snow hall. Amidst the blizzard, the door of the old clinic is left slightly open, warm light seeps through the cracks. He lazily leans against the pillar, reading through the pharmacopeia and pondering the prescriptions, until he hears footsteps nearing in the snow. The wealthy come bearing gifts, the poor come with only their clothes on them. This hall does not discriminate, there is only the doctor and the patient. With warm words and a benevolent heart, the scent of medicine spreads with the warm breeze, transforming the cold night into a melody of spring.

Name: Infernal Deliverance
Description: The Godfall Revelation — Wanshi: Lucid Dreamer
WorldDescription: Plague is the whisper of the dead, and it is my duty to silence them... forever. In the Annihilation Zone, a raven-beaked shadow roams, guiding twisted souls into eternal stillness with the blade of a scalpel. It's not salvation, he says, but the final mercy for the living.

Name: Prestigious Accolade
WorldDescription: The WGAA designed the sash and medals for this military uniform. The olive branch represents the hope for peace, while the triangular emblem is said to be inspired by the Gray Raven's insignia—its stable form is a tribute to the unbreakable bond of comrades. On the design draft, Liv added wings to the medal, turning the phoenix into a witness of eternal glory.

Name: Love's Dawn
WorldDescription: The vows exchanged at dawn demonstrate the couple's loyalty to love. When the bell rings, the pigeons chirp, and the sakura petals dance in the air, the newlyweds gently slip the rings on each other's fingers. She will be there for every moment of life with you on the journey ahead, whether it is the snow in winter or the rainbow at dawn.

Name: Rippling Luminescence
WorldDescription: Night embraces the deep sea, where tides gently lap and stardust quietly drifts down. The Milky Way gently kisses the surf, leaving bioluminescent blue shimmers that shatter and reform with the waves, like a dream too fleeting to hold. The girl stands still, letting the soft glow rise to her ankles. She gazes at the profile of the person beside her, and in that moment, it strikes her that all the beauty in the world is just like this—quiet in its arrival, yet perfectly timed.

Name: Higanbana
WorldDescription: Time dances on. An old song drifts through the empty classroom, a haunting melody. She takes a step forward, and a mirage flickers into view, shimmering and then dissolving like a soap bubble. Turning back now might spare her the torment of facing those unsettling memories. But she knows the answers she seeks lie at the heart of this labyrinth. Without a moment's hesitation, just as she did before, she steps into the sea of flowers.

Name: Candy Rider
WorldDescription: As twilight fades and the city bids farewell to the day, countless neon lights awaken. Under their glow, a girl quietly steps onto the ice rink. Unwrapping a piece of candy, she sets off with the whirring of her skates, leaving the noise and worries of the world behind as she speeds against the flow of time.

Name: Starward Dragon
WorldDescription: Where the wild lands end, a low cry breaks the silence after the sun sets behind the mountains. A dragon comes out and spreads her wings under the stars, embarking on an infinite journey against fate to awaken the slumbering world.

Name: Wings of Equilibrium
WorldDescription: The first glimmers of starlight appear along the sky's edge. A lady with a goddess-like aura sits atop a hill. Her expectant gaze is fixed on the restless sea. All of a sudden, a solitary sail breaks free from the tempest's grip, steering toward a distant horizon... Her lips curve into a faint smile as she twirls her quill, etching yet another hero's legend into her annals.

Name: Ritual of Souls
WorldDescription: Through veils of mist, the divine maiden hums a song, offering tribute to the heavens. She lowers her gaze, her fingers brushing through the sands of time, awakening spirits that have long slumbered for centuries. Amidst the fleeting mist, she seeks the answer till eternity.

Name: Nightfall Finale
WorldDescription: When eternal night draws near, the Mistress of Fate lights an undying flame. She walks through the dark corridors, sealing the glories and secrets of the past within the endless night. Through the river of time she keeps her silent watch, her crown shining like stars that never fade. She waits, for the destined one who can read the meaning behind her faint smile before time itself comes to an end.

Name: Conceited Mirage
WorldDescription: The wind brings the gentle music into the streets, putting the town to sleep. The noisy party is over. The lobby without guests seems empty. She lies on the soft sofa chair, listening to the whispers deep in her dream. The soft night has temporarily removed her tricks, but one day she will give in, letting the fire of her wild nature spread and burn through all disguises.

Name: Fatal Temptation
WorldDescription: People say a femme fatale can never truly win, yet she has found exactly what she longs for. The poor soul never had a chance to walk away unscathed—every fateful encounter beneath the late night, every meticulously planned ball... Sweet, shifting sands have already engulfed your sanity. The sharp heel of her stiletto presses against your red heart. The color of her lips is the perfect accent to the glint in her eyes. They say to stay away—but who could stop you from falling into this temptation?

Name: Roulette of Stolen Time
WorldDescription: The bone-white roulette wheel spins on, its madness never ceasing. None know when the game began, just as none can tally the souls mortgaged beneath the mountain of chips. To win everything, only to lose it all? Victory and defeat are but two faces of the same gilded Mammon Coin. As the golden flash of a card decides a fate, she smiles, gathering her opponents' fear and despair into her coffers. The house, after all, has no need for luck—only the patience to wait for the next soul to lay everything on the table.

Name: Obsidian Balladeer
WorldDescription: The girl journeys through the endless shift between day and night, expressing her feelings through the sonnet. She plucks the strings, and in the lost season, the shadow under the dim light no longer leads to the journey back. She hums along to announce the beginning of the next play.

Name: Threads of Destiny
WorldDescription: The first light of dawn softly illuminates the outlines of the mountain forest. Moss-covered stones, ancient towering trees—everything is immersed in her solemn prayer. As the ritual hymns rise and the threefold offering is presented, she gently lifts the red cup filled with vows. Warmth passes between your fingertips as you touch hers. Sharing the clear, mellow wine, you gently bind the two hearts and two futures together in a covenant. This warm bond, tied by fate, will remain harmonious and last till the end of time.

Name: Mischievous Wings
WorldDescription: Hey, here you go! What's inside? Hmm... concentrated fruit juice? And... taurine, ginseng extract, caffeine...? Is it too intense? Not at all, just drink it! You hear me? I said drink it now!

Name: Sunny Splash
WorldDescription: Waves lap against the shore beneath the girl's feet as she offers you a chilled slushie, her smile carrying a breeze of refreshment. Bathed in golden sunlight, summer's brilliance blooms in your locked gaze, transforming into radiant colors that echo in your hearts. She gathers each sparkling memory with care, cherishing them yet greedily wishing that every summer ahead could be filled with more moments spent by your side.

Name: Hollow Crown
WorldDescription: The Scorched Borderland knows night no longer as twilight hangs eternal above the Valley of Ash. The slumbering Death Knight returns from exile once more, seeking to reclaim her dominion and reforge the passage between the mortal realm and Hell. Yet, the cursed secrets within the ancient scrolls still smolder like a fire that refuses to extinguish. She lives, she blazes, she loves, and she kills—across rivers and seas, she will witness the destined ending with her own eyes.

Among the ruins of the sacred sanctuary decorated by fallen idols, she lights a candle and prays with quiet devotion, bringing peace to each soul still clinging to sorrow and resolve, refusing to be swallowed by the void.

Name: Moonweave Shorn
WorldDescription: When the moon was devoured by fog, she descended in silence. Draped in dark blue silk, her silver shears sliced through the misted glow. To her, blood sprayed across the battlefield was but brocade woven from darkness; an enemy's final breath, a thread yet unbroken. With each sweep of her blades, shards of frozen moonlight fluttered to the ground. At the edge of that severed glow, unbeknownst to all, a requiem was quietly being stitched for the souls of the fallen.

Name: Jolly Santanami
WorldDescription: A classic red and white combination with cute accessories, obviously associated to its user's preference. As for the unnecessary woolen collar... "To make Commandant warm, of course!" Said the girl with her arms wide open.

Name: Volatile Priestess
WorldDescription: This coating was recreated based on ancient legends from the database, where gods were calmed and worshipped by humans. Perhaps the wearer of this outfit would also make a suited choice in the post-apocalyptic world corrupted by Punishing.

Name: Snowbreak Bloom
WorldDescription: To send unspoken whispers toward sun-blessed petals after snow; to listen to tender words flowing beneath the shades of flowers. This is an outfit a certain maiden prepared in secrecy, all for the day of a flower viewing with you. It might still be too early, but she would still like you to be the first witness to this snow-washed spring.

Name: Bloody Love
WorldDescription: Afraid of needles? But you won’t get better without a little jab... C’mon, trust your nurse on this. It won’t hurt a bit. Pain, pain, blow away! Til the ends of milky way!

Name: Sash of Silence
WorldDescription: Beneath a sky choked with dust and blotted sun, ancient sands devour the broken steles of fallen gods. As the world-drowning dust storm swallows the last sliver of twilight, she emerges from the depths of this abyss where the dead gather. The divinities of ruin bow their heads, bestowing upon the newcomer the honor known as eternal silence. She is the shepherd who comforts all lost souls, and the general who commands death itself. She walks the fractured boundaries between existence and oblivion, gazing over the hunting grounds where eternity has fallen mute. In her realm, there is nothing—only the void's quietude, soundlessly proclaiming: death is the most ancient mercy life can receive.

Name: Lotus Ballad
WorldDescription: Under the tall window, the girl cuts and sews her own gown from soft silk, dyed in the gentle colors of mist and water, carrying the cool scent of lotus dew. In the quiet night breeze, she walks with calm steps to meet the one returning home. She lifts her hand in invitation, wishing only to stay together, to share dawn and dusk, and to watch the flowers bloom through every season.
